==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Block chain
<hw>Block chain</hw>. <fld>(Mach.)</fld> <def>A chain in which the
alternate links are broad blocks connected by thin side links pivoted to
the ends of the blocks, used with sprocket wheels to transmit power, as
in a bicycle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>blocked</ent>⟦br⟧
